label lucas_D0_A:

    "The box lands on my lap. It was shiny and warm to the touch, it was figurine-sized like any other toy..."

    "...although it weighed quite a bit more than just being plastic."

    "What's it made of?"

    "This toy felt different."

    "The design of the box looked like it had gold leaf embedded around it that were shaped like stars."

    "I was planning on getting a snack before all this. My tummy grumbled loud. What should I eat?"

