label lucas_D0_AA:

    "I get up and place the box on the table of my PC. I go to my kitchen to grab my half eaten tub of vanilla Ice Cream."

    "I came back to sit in front of the box. I brought a spoonful of ice cream to my lips, and a melted piece of the ice cream fell."

    "I gasped as I saw it fall down heading for the box."

    "It lands beside it on the table with a splat."

    mc "Phew!"

    "I sigh with relief. The box is safe."

