label lucas_D0_AB:

    "I get up and place the box on my PC table. I reach for my snack pile to grab a Cheetoes Puff."

    "I rip the top open and pop one in my mouth."

    mc "Mmmmm... cheetoes..."

    "I eat up almost half of the pack."

    "Okay, I'm getting kinda full. Let's unbox!"

    "I don't brush off the Cheetoes crumbs from my fingers. I grab the box with my cheetoes crumbs hands."

    "I smeared the damp crust around the box of my figurine. I take the figurine out of the box and inspect it."

    mc "Oooo! He's so pretty!"

    "I grab hold of the figurine with my dirty hands."

    jump lucas_D0_B

label lucas_D0_AC:

    "I place the box on my PC table and I reach for my snack pile and grab a pack of Pumpkin seeds."

    mc "Let's eat something light and healthy."

    "I grab a seed and pop it in my mouth. I chew it in my mouth."

    "There was a trashcan right beside my table, I spit it out in the general direction not caring where it landed and thought that I'd clean it up after anyways."

    "Which I almost never do."

    "I'm not the best aim and I accidentally fired at the box."

    "The seed landed on the side of the box with a splat made from my saliva. I don't realize until I've had my fill."

    "I got back to the box and to my surprise, seeds were stuck to the box and on my desk."

    mc "Oops."

    "I dust it off the box and proceed to open it. The cardboard was soggy in some parts."

    jump lucas_D0_B

label lucas_D0_B:

    "I open the box with excitement. I see the very intricate details on the figurine."

    "His hair was strikingly bright yellow with star shapes on his side bangs."

    mc "What a strange hairstyle."

    "His eyes were red as rubies and he had iris the shape of stars with four points."

    "His suit was tailored and customized with stars the same patterns as his eyes."

    "Everything about this character was intricate. He was striking a pose holding a golden coin."

    mc "Is he from an anime?"

    "I place him on the table in my living room and I continue to admire him. I look for the box and find out if he has a name."

    "I found the words written in gold {i}“Lucas de Beaumont”.{/i}"

    mc "Hello Lucas, you're so pretty! You have such dazzling eyes and shiny hair!"

    "I fuss over him and fiddle with his hair and brush it a bit to undo the stars but it wont come undone."

    "I tried out every nook and cranny of the figure, from trying to pose him to trying to grab his coin. I found the doll was merely only for display."

    "I don't mind since it's pretty and the figure was a cutie and just my type. He looked like a villain from an anime."

    "After fiddling with the figure for a bit, it got later into the night. I left it on the top of the coffee table in the living room and I headed to bed."



